%t A101168 Length/@SubstitutionSystem[{a->{a,a,b},b->{a,a,c},c->a},{a},15] (* The program generates the first 16 terms of the sequence. To generate more, increase the final ("15") constant. *) (* _Harvey P. Dale_, Sep 05 2022 *)
